{"tid":1764890,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【黃色經濟圈】一齊做大個餅佢，想知各樣零售/文化/玩樂嘅黃店請入黎！","createTime":"2019-12-01T12:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T16:05:50.000Z","uid":301438,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c0beff00de8d0e351cc456fcf0ec7fd48df8700e","tid":1764890,"uid":301438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:28:52.000Z","msg":"《Kongazine 港介線》上線喇！<br />\n<br />\n大家好，我哋係一條全新嘅網上頻道，透過專訪香港大街小巷、不同行業<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">包括零售、文化、運動等嘅黃色小店</span></span>💛，希望協助大家係支持黃餐廳之餘，都可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">懲罰不同產業嘅黃店</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">進一步擴大黃色經濟圈🤩</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n我地已陸續訪問緊唔同行業嘅店鋪💁&zwj;♀️，想知有咩良心商店等住您狠狠咁去懲罰佢，記得<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">like👍🏻&amp;follow我地既FB同IG喇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB/IG: @kongazine<br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/kongazine?igshid=rzh7u6677qb3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fkongazine%3Figshid%3Drzh7u6677qb3&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=aceaa496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/kongazine?igshid=rzh7u6677qb3</a><br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kongazine/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkongazine%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=6440b3f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kongazine/</a><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 第一段訪問片將會係今晚稍後推出喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果您有任何新奇有趣既黃店想推介俾我地，歡迎留言🙇🏼&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️可能下一間訪問既黃店就係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#煲底見 <br />\n#光復香港 #時代革命 <br />\n#良心小店 #良心小店專訪<br />\n#黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n同時誠邀加入我地-文宣/設計/拍片/採訪/剪接/寫稿，有興趣請telegram @LokL0K<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OaJ6PqW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOaJ6PqW.jpg&h=8a5281cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7949a61587b8bb226e4e38f81093bffbec8cb29","tid":1764890,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:29:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31378651644c65aad02d4f28456a46b15adc4758","tid":1764890,"uid":210608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:31:14.000Z","msg":"有個問題，d租金最尾係咪去番藍到？"},{"pid":"43278e78e2a22ce4673e2598e2c4911639caac5b","tid":1764890,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31378651644c65aad02d4f28456a46b15adc4758","tid":1764890,"uid":210608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:31:14.000Z","msg":"有個問題，d租金最尾係咪去番藍到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774d7f3c43deeccf3866f7c9986d866f6ef6e085","tid":1764890,"uid":247878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:37:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f5afa7bdbdcfca30dc2e6806ea5fcf96ad7854c","tid":1764890,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99f4659c014dc9bc56a1dc2ef7f1437f55f3ffec","tid":1764890,"uid":85751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31378651644c65aad02d4f28456a46b15adc4758","tid":1764890,"uid":210608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:31:14.000Z","msg":"有個問題，d租金最尾係咪去番藍到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:42:19.000Z","msg":"你諗到咁乜都唔洗做啦"},{"pid":"ca020c684b8a286578e3e0f455ac0e5956109ec5","tid":1764890,"uid":882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31378651644c65aad02d4f28456a46b15adc4758","tid":1764890,"uid":210608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:31