/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賺錢呢我地就唔分顏色o既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時就盡量幫藍老闆駛錢落黃店度喇，聖誕PARTY訂到會、抽獎、交換禮物、送客果籃朱古力、春茗，日常廁紙咖啡電腦 OUTSOURCE VENDORs<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8547e00f49b9d84af1c0f52b071a4b1248bc8c8a","tid":1764890,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"[黃色經濟圈] 時代革命由生活開始：黃色商圈已降臨（劉細良）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1766519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1766519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}